    <abstract>
      <t>This document proposes extending BMP to allow BMP messages with the
   per-peer header to carry interface information for the established
   peer session, especially in order to distinguish parallel link-local
   and unnumbered BGP peers established based on distinct interfaces.</t>
    </abstract>
